The paper introduces a new modelling language for NP-complete search problems based on concepts of functional programming. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI), programming languages (cs.PL), logic (cs.LO), data structures (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE).
